This was a huge disappointment, especially since I increased the quantities to make this for 10 people. The cream and white chocolate (imported from Switzerland) combined to make a very slimy mouth feel. The lime juice separated from the whipped cream mixture upon standing, so leftovers were appalling. I spent $25 on this dessert and would have done much better spending the money on a gorgeous cake from a bakery.

