This is our family's traditional Christmas dessert; I started making it when my first baby was 2 yrs. (and underfoot each step in the kitchen!); now she is 4 yrs. and loves to help me assemble these beautifully, deliciously simple treats. Occasionally, we make them in the summertime when we are wistful for the holidays.

