I made this for dinner guests last night. They couldn't stop raving about it. I will definitely make this again. It is easy, the presentation is beautiful and the flavor is outrageous. I was worried that my fruit was too tart but the fool balanced the flavors perfectly. I followed the recipe exactly and I wouldn't change a thing. It's a perfect spring/summer dessert.

